# Convert json to sting (usable form as json value)
i.e. wrap entire json in double quote and escape each quote inside json.
```sh
jq tostring <file>
```
This command changes
```json
{
    "a": "apple",
    "b": "banana"
}
```
to
```
"{\"a\":\"apple\",\"b\":\"banana\"}"
```

# Convert escaped json to normal json (invert of tostring)
```sh
jq fromjson <file>
```

